OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782199088
OL,3,CAndy Burnham sworn in as Makerfield MP
OL,5,FAndy Burnham was officially sworn in a
OL,6,FMP for Makerfield on Monday.
OL,8,FAndy Burnham was given a hero's
OL,9,Fwelcome by Labour MPs at Westminster
OL,10,Fas he was official sworn in as an MP
OL,11,Ffollowing his emphatic by-election win.
OL,13,FThe new Makerfield MP was welcomed
OL,14,Finto the hall with a round of applause
OL,15,Fwhere one MP yelled "Rome is saved",
OL,16,Fbefore another on the opposing bench
OL,17,Fheckled, "he's not the messiah".
OL,19,FNodding to Monty Python's Life of
OL,20,FBrian, Mr Burnham replied: "Naughty
OL,21,Fboy."
OL,26,@yD@JOUyD@_O]|D@\OU}D@EO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
