CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782199088
OL,3,CAndy Burnham sworn in as Makerfield MP
OL,5,FBurnham later posed for pictures with
OL,6,Fscores of his new parliamentary
OL,7,Fcolleagues including Wes Streeting,
OL,8,Fthe former health secretary who had
OL,9,Fbeen seen as his main rival for the
OL,10,Fleadership before throwing his weight
OL,11,Fbehind him following Starmer's
OL,12,Fresignation.
OL,14,FFormer armed forces minister Al Carns,
OL,15,Fanother potential leadership
OL,16,Fcandidate, was also among the MPs in
OL,17,FParliament's mediaeval Westminster
OL,18,FHall for the return of the King of the
OL,19,FNorth.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
