FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782199088
OL,3,CAndy Burnham sworn in as Makerfield MP
OL,5,FChancellor Rachel Reeves, Energy
OL,6,FSecretary Ed Miliband and chief whip
OL,7,FJonathan Reynolds were among the
OL,8,FCabinet ministers at the photo call,
OL,9,Falong with former deputy prime
OL,10,Fminister Angela Rayner.
OL,12,FBurnham could be prime minister by mid-
OL,13,FJuly if no other challenger emerges
OL,14,Ffollowing Sir Keir Starmer's decision
OL,15,Fto quit as Labour leader on 22 June.
OL,17,FThe public show of support for Burnham
OL,18,Fsuggests little appetite for a contest
OL,19,F- he could now be on course to enter
OL,20,F10 Downing Street within weeks.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
