PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782199088
OL,3,CAndy Burnham sworn in as Makerfield MP
OL,5,FStarmer made an emotional resignation
OL,6,Fand acknowledged he had lost the
OL,7,Fsupport of his MPs and promised an
OL,8,F"orderly handover of power" to his
OL,9,Fsuccessor.
OL,11,FPotential candidates have until
OL,12,Fnominations for a new leader close on
OL,13,F16 July to amass the support of at
OL,14,Fleast 81 Labour MPs.
OL,16,FBut if Burnham is the only candidate
OL,17,Fto receive the support needed, he
OL,18,Fcould become prime minister on either
OL,19,F17 or 18 July.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@[O]
