OL,3,CAndy Burnham sworn in as Makerfield MP
OL,5,FBurnham played down the prospect of
OL,6,Fcalling a snap general election if he
OL,7,Fbecomes prime minister in chaotic
OL,8,Fscenes as he arrived at London's
OL,9,FEuston station.
OL,11,F"You're jumping several hurdles ahead
OL,12,Fthere," he told reporters waiting for
OL,13,Fhis late-running train from Manchester.
OL,15,FHis arrival in Parliament was met with
OL,16,Fa small protest, including calls of
OL,17,F"traitor" as he got out of the taxi
OL,18,Fthat had carried him from London's
OL,19,FEuston station.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@GO]yD@AOUyD@IO]
