OL,3,CAndy Burnham sworn in as Makerfield MP
OL,5,FHe swept through the parliamentary
OL,6,Festate escorted by security guards,
OL,7,Fpausing to say hello to Labour MPs
OL,8,Fincluding former defence secretary
OL,9,FJohn Healey who embraced him.
OL,11,FReform UK leader Nigel Farage called
OL,12,Ffor a general election in the wake of
OL,13,FSir Keir's resignation, tweeting: "If
OL,14,FLabour thinks it can shove another
OL,15,Fprofessional politician into No 10, it
OL,16,Fhas another thing coming."
OL,26,@uD@cOUxD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
