PN,36807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782199088
OL,3,CAndy Burnham sworn in as Makerfield MP
OL,5,FTory leader Kemi Badenoch said there
OL,6,Fshould be an election "if Andy Burnham
OL,7,Fis not able to set out how he's going
OL,8,Fto keep our country safe" amid an
OL,9,Fongoing row within government over
OL,10,Fdefence funding.
OL,12,FOther opposition figures stopped short
OL,13,Fof demanding an election, but urged
OL,14,FSir Keir's successor to be bold.
OL,16,FLiberal Democrat leader Sir Ed Davey
OL,17,Fsaid: "Whoever becomes prime minister
OL,18,Fneeds to drop the caution and
OL,19,Fcomplacency and show the ambition our
OL,20,Fcountry deserves."
OL,26,@nD@WOUpD@YO]yD@GOU|D@RO]
